                <p>

Art of Artesian’s goal is to provide income opportunities to  female artisans and bring economic stability and prosperity to their families. The program model for this project is based on evidence based research proving how economic stability impact the education, health and well-being of a household. The group of female artisans that supply crafts to the project live in rural and coastal communities in the Sindh-Balochistan region, they carved off time to create these products after finishing their chores, most sacrifices socializations and social events to create these products to bring in a second income to their family.  
